{"tid":1277280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逆向思維 手錶時間問題。一定要思想免疫","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:39:08.000Z","uid":19817,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47a021c4f70981b08893e07cd142c93c59d05fd0","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"一個警察發言人出鏡前全身既野都會有人執過<br />\n更何況現在係非常時期 隻錶會冇check過？<br />\n<br />\n呢個根本就係陷阱黎 想分化前線有鬼<br />\n<br />\n市民琴晚團結一致去完成創舉<br />\n係令到上層係十分震驚 連侵侵都嚇左一跳<br />\n<br />\n事實證明市民做緊既野令上層極度不安<br />\n市民既路線係岩既 狗官不斷屌就岩架喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>永遠支持同相信前線既集體捨命決定<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"99d0e055b749b29d3a7eab1fd297d20139da94ac","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39d9e72a7fc707587c80048df034217ddba6b71","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7315edeb4f6d61c33e9c274634661f52ff892b6f","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65e34b66f245c0bb552d2ddf5224de59b63234e6","tid":1277280,"uid":81424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"前綫冇鬼<br />\n係警察設局跣人<br />\n想包抄香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知畀人頂住晒"},{"pid":"f851dc57d55f8b2a7cdb0972abc72f812bb16130","tid":1277280,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"鬼預你影到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢自己睇時間仲重要啦"},{"pid":"09f00afa21f1ecb42fdcf98af8cd38be1c3f2836","tid":1277280,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭玩緊共匪老技倆，拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派五毛做打手，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次佢不斷鬧示威者暴力，就係想班三姑六婆一齊鬧埋一份，造成世代之爭，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持頭腦清晰，和理非同勇武都係一齊合作嘅同伴，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易中咗政府同五毛嘅分化計"},{"pid":"0887e36c9d394f50260099a86d14450526d66978","tid":1277280,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:40:10.000Z","msg":"佢一早預你衝入去<br />\n反正自己會放軟手腳<br />\n企哂係閘後面都係做比記者睇姐<br />\n一開閘就跑住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebe9f30f355dc136656f275757dc7bc7260965","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"我知呀 <br />\n<br />\n但佢叫三毛/引你地講佢地係有人配合<br />\n去製造懷疑<br />\n所以咩都唔洗理 笑7佢地就得"},{"pid":"f7f237113cfaf7e67bd2750d5df641df4c0d1ac3","tid":1277280,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"個場只要犬隻走晒無人擋就入到啦,拍定真係無問題喎,唔想OT嘛"},{"pid":"cc194a1853d67290419958aac28ff05625459357","tid":1277280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefed30c49a96eb4ec0902d0dc976465e39e0ac9","tid":1277280,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"陣間佢話 一早預定會有唔同情況發生拍定幾條片 真係吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif